<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="en"><head><meta charset="UTF-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"><title>Error 404 - Local | AwardSpace.com</title><link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@300;400;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"><style>*, *::before, *::after{ box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0;}:root{--red:rgba(255, 2, 40, 0.85);--blue:#3564ff;--blue-glow:rgba(53, 100, 255, 0.22);--ink:#111;--mist:#f4f7fb;}html, body{min-height:100%;font-family:'Montserrat', sans-serif;color:var(--ink);background:#fff;}/* ── Hero ── */.hero{position:relative;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;min-height:78vh;padding:60px 24px;text-align:center;overflow:hidden;background-image:repeating-radial-gradient(circle at center, rgba(255,2,40,.07) 0, #fff 55%, #fff 60%, rgba(53,100,255,.15) 100%);}.error-code{font-family:'Montserrat', sans-serif;font-size:clamp(3.5rem, 10vw, 7rem);font-weight:800;color:var(--blue);letter-spacing:-2px;line-height:1;margin-bottom:20px;}.hero > *{ position:relative;z-index:1;}.badge{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;padding:5px 14px;border-radius:100px;border:1px solid rgba(255,2,40,.3);background:rgba(255,2,40,.05);color:var(--red);font-size:.68rem;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:28px;}.badge::before{content:'';width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--red);animation:pulse 1.8s ease-in-out infinite;}@keyframes pulse{0%, 100%{ opacity:1;transform:scale(1);}50%{ opacity:.4;transform:scale(.6);}}h1{font-family:'Montserrat', sans-serif;font-size:clamp(1.6rem, 4vw, 2.8rem);line-height:1.2;max-width:640px;margin-bottom:16px;font-weight:700;}.sub{font-size:.95rem;color:#556;max-width:400px;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:36px;font-weight:300;}.btn-primary{display:inline-block;padding:14px 32px;background:var(--blue);color:#fff;text-decoration:none;border-radius:8px;font-family:'Montserrat', sans-serif;font-weight:600;font-size:.9rem;letter-spacing:.02em;box-shadow:0 1px 6px 0 rgb(12 113 195 / 91%);transition:opacity .18s;}.btn-primary:hover{ opacity:.88;}/* ── Cards ── */.cards-section{background:var(--mist);padding:60px 24px 80px;min-height:65vh;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;}.cards-section h2{text-align:center;font-family:'Montserrat', sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1.3rem;margin-bottom:40px;color:#223;}.cards{display:flex;gap:118px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;max-width:950px;margin:0 auto;}.card{background:#fff;border-radius:16px;padding:36px 32px;flex:1;min-width:260px;border:1px solid transparent;box-shadow:none;transition:box-shadow .22s, border-color .22s;position:relative;overflow:hidden;}.card:hover{border-color:rgba(53,100,255,.2);box-shadow:0 8px 32px rgba(53,100,255,.13);}.card-icon{width:42px;height:42px;border-radius:10px;background:rgba(53,100,255,.08);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:20px;}.card-icon svg{ width:20px;height:20px;stroke:var(--blue);fill:none;stroke-width:1.8;stroke-linecap:round;stroke-linejoin:round;}.card h3{font-family:'Montserrat', sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1.15rem;margin-bottom:10px;line-height:1.35;}.card p{font-size:1.1rem;color:#667;line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:24px;font-weight:400;}.btn-card{display:inline-block;padding:10px 22px;border-radius:7px;border:1.5px solid var(--blue);color:var(--blue);text-decoration:none;font-size:.85rem;font-weight:600;transition:background .18s, color .18s;}.btn-card:hover{ background:var(--blue);color:#fff;}/* ── Footer ── */footer{text-align:center;padding:32px 24px;background:#fff;font-size:.8rem;color:#889;border-top:1px solid #eef0f5;font-weight:400;}footer a{ color:var(--blue);text-decoration:none;font-weight:600;}footer a:hover{ text-decoration:underline;}</style></head><body><section class="hero"><div class="badge">Not Found</div><div class="error-code">404</div><h1>The Page You are Looking for Doesn't Exist.</h1><p class="sub">The page may have been moved, deleted, or never existed in the first place.</p><a class="btn-primary" href="https://www.awardspace.com/free-hosting/">Start Your Website for Free</a></section><section class="cards-section"><h2>You can also check out these options!</h2><div class="cards"><div class="card"><div class="card-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M3 12l2-2m0 0l7-7 7 7M5 10v10a1 1 0 001 1h3m10-11l2 2m-2-2v10a1 1 0 01-1 1h-3m-6 0a1 1 0 001-1v-4a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v4a1 1 0 001 1m-6 0h6"/></svg></div><h3>Start with Premium Hosting</h3><p>Getting Premium Shared Hosting will unlock all available features, more disk space, and bandwidth. Right now, premium is just $2.99 for the first year!</p><a class="btn-card" href="https://www.awardspace.com/web-hosting/">Learn more</a></div><div class="card"><div class="card-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5zM2 17l10 5 10-5M2 12l10 5 10-5"/></svg></div><h3>Learn How to Create a WordPress Website</h3><p>If you want to have your own website but don't know how to build it, here is the full guide on how to Create a website with WordPress.</p><a class="btn-card" href="https://www.awardspace.com/wordpress-tutorials/create-a-wordpress-website/">Learn WordPress</a></div></div></section><footer>If you're not 100% satisfied with AwardSpace, we'll refund your payment. &nbsp;·&nbsp;<a href="https://www.awardspace.com/">AwardSpace.com</a></footer></body></html>#EXTINF:-1,ESPN HD [US] --> SPORTTV
